      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain remains perfectly shimmed, and the Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled for optimal cam phasing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the original suspension geometry is preserved. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
